PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774617128
OL,3,C'Disgusting' decision to test daughter
OL,4,Cfor drugs after stabbing, says dad
OL,6,FThe father of one of the Nottingham
OL,7,Fattacks victims has told an inquiry it
OL,8,Fis "disgusting" that the teenage
OL,9,Fstabbing victims were tested for drugs
OL,10,Fand alcohol but their killer was not.
OL,12,FSanjoy Kumar, Grace O'Malley-Kumar's
OL,13,Ffather, said he could not understand
OL,14,Fwhy their killer, paranoid
OL,15,Fschizophrenic Valdo Calocane, had not
OL,16,Fbeen tested for drugs while he was in
OL,17,Fcustody after going on a violent
OL,18,Frampage in Nottingham.
OL,26,@pD@DOUpD@OO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774617128
OL,3,C'Disgusting' decision to test daughter
OL,4,Cfor drugs after stabbing, says dad
OL,6,FMs O'Malley-Kumar, 19, was stabbed to
OL,7,Fdeath with her university friend
OL,8,FBarnaby Webber in the early hours of
OL,9,F13 June 2023 in Ilkeston Road after
OL,10,Fgoing on a night out.
OL,12,FCalocane then killed caretaker Ian
OL,13,FCoates, 65, before running over three
OL,14,Fpedestrians with a stolen van.
OL,16,FDr Kumar said he had to sign human
OL,17,Ftissue forms ` forms he had never seen
OL,18,Fhimself as a GP and a forensic medical
OL,19,Fexaminer with the Metropolitan Police
OL,20,F` otherwise their daughter's body
OL,21,Fwould not be released to them.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774617128
OL,3,C'Disgusting' decision to test daughter
OL,4,Cfor drugs after stabbing, says dad
OL,6,FDr Kumar told the central London
OL,7,Finquiry: "You had to sign them, but
OL,8,Fwhat was not highlighted was that this
OL,9,Fis a point in time where you are also
OL,10,Fsigning to say that samples could be
OL,11,Ftaken. That was absolutely not pointed
OL,12,Fout.
OL,14,F"They took samples from our children
OL,15,Fto test for drugs and alcohol. I was
OL,16,Freally struck by that being really
OL,17,Fquite disgusting.
OL,26,@oD@JOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774617128
OL,3,C'Disgusting' decision to test daughter
OL,4,Cfor drugs after stabbing, says dad
OL,6,F"Our children were tested, but the
OL,7,Fculprit wasn't and from there on in,
OL,8,Fin terms of previous interactions and
OL,9,Fmental health, that was not made into
OL,10,Fa big thing at all, that was a flyaway
OL,11,Fcomment."
OL,13,FDr Kumar "just couldn't understand"
OL,14,Fthat a hair sample was not taken while
OL,15,Fkiller Valdo Calocane was in custody,
OL,16,Fadding "it may have proved nothing but
OL,17,Fit may have proved everything".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@IO]uD@JOUuD@cO]xD@HOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774617128
OL,3,C'Disgusting' decision to test daughter
OL,4,Cfor drugs after stabbing, says dad
OL,6,FThe father said that from his
OL,7,Fexperience he knew a hair sample to
OL,8,Ftest for drugs did not require
OL,9,FCalocane's consent.
OL,11,FRetired Nottinghamshire Police
OL,12,FDetective Superintendent Leigh Sanders
OL,13,Fpreviously apologised to bereaved
OL,14,Ffamilies during the inquiry for a
OL,15,Fdecision not to take a hair sample to
OL,16,Ftest Calocane for possible drug use.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774617128
OL,3,C'Disgusting' decision to test daughter
OL,4,Cfor drugs after stabbing, says dad
OL,6,FBut the ex-officer said that a sample
OL,7,Fof hair "would not be able to provide
OL,8,Fanalysis that showed drugs or alcohol
OL,9,Fin the system at a specific time or
OL,10,Fdate".
OL,12,FDr Kumar said: "If you're a detective
OL,13,Fof any description at all, and I think
OL,14,Fevery detective watching this is going
OL,15,Fto agree, if you are here to detect
OL,16,Fcrime, that means forensics is really
OL,17,Fimportant.
OL,19,F"And a basic part of that forensics is
OL,20,Fhead hair."
OL,26,@oD@IOUrD@EO]tD@POU{D@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774617128
OL,3,C'Disgusting' decision to test daughter
OL,4,Cfor drugs after stabbing, says dad
OL,6,FDr Kumar said it is "obvious" that if
OL,7,FCalocane, who was the subject of a
OL,8,Fwarrant after assaulting a police
OL,9,Fofficer, had been arrested before the
OL,10,Fattacks, there would have been a
OL,11,Fdifferent outcome.
OL,13,FHe told the inquiry: "The analogy I
OL,14,Fuse with VC (Valdo Calocane) is that
OL,15,FVC was like an oil tanker who crashed
OL,16,Finto our children and Ian. A one-
OL,17,Fdegree change in his course, he could
OL,18,Fhave ended up in a different
OL,19,Fcontinent."
OL,26,@nD@UOUnD@]O]uD@VOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774617128
OL,3,C'Disgusting' decision to test daughter
OL,4,Cfor drugs after stabbing, says dad
OL,6,FHe added: "If he'd missed our
OL,7,Fchildren, he would've hit someone
OL,8,Felse's."
OL,10,FDr Kumar said the family went for a
OL,11,Fmeeting with the Independent Office
OL,12,Ffor Police Conduct (IOPC) with faith
OL,13,Fin the organisation but found it
OL,14,F"absurd" when a decision-maker in the
OL,15,Fmeeting decided to hold a prayer.
OL,17,FHe told the inquiry: "The IOPC have
OL,18,Fbeen unprofessional and nothing but a
OL,19,Fjoke. When people say they are not fit
OL,20,Ffor purpose, I believe that.
OL,26,@nD@KOUpD@HO]vD@AOUvD@HO]yD@VOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774617128
OL,3,C'Disgusting' decision to test daughter
OL,4,Cfor drugs after stabbing, says dad
OL,6,F"We had a meeting and the decision-
OL,7,Fmaker held a prayer in the room when
OL,8,Fwe walked in. It was the most absurd
OL,9,Fthing I have ever seen in my life.
OL,11,F"We were asking serious questions and
OL,12,Fthe decision-maker said 'let's say a
OL,13,Fprayer'. It was absurd."
OL,15,FOn Wednesday morning, Mr Webber's
OL,16,Fparents said they will "never forgive"
OL,17,Fthe police after officers accessed
OL,18,Ffootage from the attacks and sent
OL,19,FWhatsApp messages about their son's
OL,20,Finjuries.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@XO]xD@XOUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774617128
OL,3,C'Disgusting' decision to test daughter
OL,4,Cfor drugs after stabbing, says dad
OL,6,FHis mother Emma Webber described one
OL,7,Fmessage as "disgusting and grotesque".
OL,9,FDavid Webber, the student's father,
OL,10,Fsaid: "And it does seem to me that,
OL,11,Fagain, in this case, my son, who was
OL,12,Fthe victim here, his privacy was not
OL,13,Ftaken into consideration."
OL,15,FMr and Mrs Webber described the
OL,16,F"unfolding horror" of learning that
OL,17,Fprosecutors intended to accept
OL,18,FCalocane's plea of guilty to
OL,19,Fmanslaughter.
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@eO]rD@GOUuD@ZO]xD@AOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774617128
OL,3,C'Disgusting' decision to test daughter
OL,4,Cfor drugs after stabbing, says dad
OL,6,FMr Webber said: "It's a bit of a state
OL,7,Fof shock because you've set yourself
OL,8,Fup for 'this is what we're doing:
OL,9,Fthree counts of murder, three counts
OL,10,Fof attempted murder'.
OL,12,F"Then all of a sudden it's a complete
OL,13,FU-turn."
OL,15,FCalocane, who admitted manslaughter
OL,16,Fand attempted murder, is detained
OL,17,Findefinitely in a high-security
OL,18,Fhospital after prosecutors accepted
OL,19,Fhis not guilty pleas to murder on the
OL,20,Fgrounds of diminished responsibility
OL,21,Fin January 2024.
OL,26,@nD@QOUtD@AOUuD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
